description.detailed_description: A dark brown user interface panel with rounded corners is centrally displayed, featuring a welcome message and multiple interactive buttons. It overlays a blurred, textured background reminiscent of a fantasy map. The lighting is even, and the overall mood is inviting and informative, typical of a game's dialogue or menu screen.
description.text_content:
THE ELDER
A gentle welcome
Welcome, traveler. This town holds pieces of Yash's journey. Where would you like to go?
Tell me about Yash
Show me his projects
What skills does he have?
How can I contact him?
I'll explore on my own
